org.freezedry.persistence.containers.orderedseries

Class TaggedOrderedSeries<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<TaggedOrderedSeries.Entry<T,V>>
      • org.freezedry.persistence.containers.orderedseries.TaggedOrderedSeries<T,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<TaggedOrderedSeries.Entry<T,V>>, java.util.Collection<TaggedOrderedSeries.Entry<T,V>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicOrderedSeries, IntegerOrderedSeries, UnmodifiableTaggedOrderedSeries

    public class TaggedOrderedSeries<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>,V>
extends java.util.AbstractCollection<TaggedOrderedSeries.Entry<T,V>>
    Dec 23, 2009 Ordered time series based on the natural ordering of keys (T). Provides insertion into the time series based on natural ordering of the keys. Allows forward and reverse iteration from specified starting points. All keys must implement Comparable< T > and follow the intended semantics.
